de.weltraumschaf.commons.shell

Class LiteralCommandMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.weltraumschaf.commons.shell.LiteralCommandMap

  • public abstract class LiteralCommandMap
extends Object
    Maps the literal string of an command to its enum type. This class is not thread safe!
    Author:
    Sven Strittmatter

      • determineCommand

        public final MainCommandType determineCommand(Token<String> t)
        Determines the appropriate main command type for given string token. You should check with isCommand(de.weltraumschaf.commons.shell.Token) before invocation. Determining a non command token string will result in an exception.
        Parameters:
        t - token to check
        Returns:
        command main type // CHECKSTYLE:OFF
